reef (0.3.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Persistence modes (state, full) for cross-command bash state
  * Confirm mode — preview translations before executing
  * Library crate — reef is now both a binary and a Rust library
  * 498 unit tests + 11 doc tests, zero clippy warnings

